label: uncl9417
comment: Code specifying a type of government action such as inspection, detention, fumigation, security.

values.label: Clearance
values.comment: The cargo will be or has been cleared.

values.label: Detention
values.comment: The cargo has been or will be detained.

values.label: Fumigation
values.comment: The cargo has been or will be fumigated.

values.label: Inspection
values.comment: The cargo has been or will be inspected.

values.label: Security
values.comment: The cargo has been or will be secured.

values.label: Means of transport admittance
values.comment: The means of transport will be or has been admitted.

values.label: Cargo hold inspection
values.comment: The cargo hold has been or will be inspected.

values.label: Container inspection
values.comment: The container has been or will be inspected.

values.label: Cargo packaging inspection
values.comment: The cargo packaging has been or will be inspected.

values.label: Export certificate not required
values.comment: Indication by exporter that they do not need certificate of export from Customs.
